Package com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.points

Class FillerArrayPoints<T extends java.lang.Number>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.Filler<Array<T>>
      • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.FillerArray<Point<T>>
        • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.points.FillerArrayPoints<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of coordinates encapsulated in the object of the Point class.
    public class FillerArrayPoints<T extends java.lang.Number>
extends FillerArray<Point<T>>
    The class is the inheritor of the class FillerArray.

    The class that is a container that encapsulates a specific implementation of a contract declared in the FillingArrayPointsArrayNumbers interface and delegates to it an obligation to perform functionality to fills an object of the Array class and classical array of object of the Point class with numeric coordinates.

    Created by Konstantin Lugowoy on 16-Jan-18.

    Version:
    1.3
    Author:
    Konstantin Lugowoy
    See Also:
    Filler, FillerArray, Filling, FillingArray
